> <@nicolo-ribaudo:matrix.org> If wrappers are immutable, `Record(wrapper)`

Not 100% sure why that is a requirement:
```js
var obj = Object(1);
obj.x = 2;
obj.x; // 2
var i = Number(obj);
i; // 1
i.x; // undefined
```

